item.title: When Bill Russell witnessed Wilt Chamberlain Manhandling One of Strongest Players of All-time
item.description: When Bill Russell witnessed Wilt Chamberlain Manhandling One of Strongest Players of All-time Wilt Chamberlain has often been described as one of the strongest and most athletic NBA stars of all time and has Bill Russell vouching for him.
